de.jaret.util.ui.timebars.swing.renderer

接口 GridRenderer

  • 所有已知实现类:
    DefaultGridRenderer

    public interface GridRenderer
    Interface for supplying a JComponent used to render the grid in a TimeBarViewer. The component should be parametrized using the access methods of the viewer and should be reused for subsequent paint calls.
    版本:
    $Id: GridRenderer.java 835 2009-02-14 21:03:52Z kliem $
    作者:
    Peter Kliem
